<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TicTacToe-KI · Code-Lernpfad</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

:root{
  --bg: #06080f;
  --bg-elevated: #0b0f1c;
  --panel: #0e1424;
  --panel-border: #1d2740;
  --grid-line: rgba(120,150,255,0.06);
  --cyan: #5ee7ff;
  --violet: #9b6dff;
  --magenta: #ff5ec0;
  --text-hi: #eef1ff;
  --text-mid: #9aa6c8;
  --text-low: #5c6688;
  --code-bg: #080b14;
  --success: #5cffb0;
  --error: #ff6b81;
  --warn: #ffd166;
  --font-display: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --radius: 14px;
  --transition: 0.35s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
}

*{ box-sizing: border-box; }
html{ scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body{
  margin:0;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text-hi);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  line-height: 1.6;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Ambient background grid */
body::before{
  content:"";
  position: fixed;
  inset:0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 48px 48px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index:0;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, black 40%, transparent 90%);
}

body::after{
  content:"";
  position: fixed;
  top:-20%; left:50%;
  width:140%; height:60%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(94,231,255,0.10), transparent 60%);
  pointer-events:none;
  z-index:0;
}

a{ color: var(--cyan); }

h1,h2,h3,h4{
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0 0 .5em 0;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}

code, pre, .mono{ font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.wrap{
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 980px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
}

/* ============ Scroll progress bar ============ */
#progress-bar{
  position: fixed;
  top:0; left:0;
  height: 3px;
  width:0%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet), var(--magenta));
  z-index: 999;
  transition: width .1s linear;
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(94,231,255,.6);
}

/* ============ Nav ============ */
nav{
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 900;
  padding: 18px 24px;
  display:flex;
  gap: 10px;
  align-items:center;
}
.nav-pill{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  background: rgba(14,20,36,0.7);
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  padding: 8px 14px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
}
.nav-dot{
  width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;
  background: var(--success);
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--success);
  animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse-dot{ 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:.4;} }

/* ============ Hero ============ */
.hero{
  min-height: 92vh;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
  position: relative;
  padding-top: 60px;
}
.eyebrow{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--cyan);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.eyebrow .bracket{ color: var(--text-low); }

.hero h1{
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
  line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--text-hi);
  max-width: 760px;
}
.hero h1 .grad{
  background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet) 55%, var(--magenta));
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  background-clip: text;
  color: transparent;
}
.hero p.lead{
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  max-width: 620px;
  margin-top: 18px;
}

.hero-board-stage{
  margin-top: 48px;
  display:flex;
  gap: 40px;
  align-items:center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* Decorative circuit board signature element */
.circuit-board{
  width: 220px;
  height: 220px;
  position: relative;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.circuit-board svg{ width:100%; height:100%; }
.circuit-cell-line{ stroke: var(--panel-border); stroke-width: 1.5; }
.circuit-node{
  fill: var(--bg-elevated);
  stroke: var(--text-low);
  stroke-width: 1.2;
}
.circuit-trace{
  fill:none;
  stroke: var(--cyan);
  stroke-width: 2;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px var(--cyan));
  stroke-dasharray: 6 4;
  animation: trace-flow 3s linear infinite;
  opacity: 0.85;
}
.circuit-trace.v{ stroke: var(--magenta); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px var(--magenta)); animation-delay: -1.2s;}
@keyframes trace-flow{ to{ stroke-dashoffset: -100; } }

.hero-meta{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  max-width: 320px;
}
.hero-meta strong{ color: var(--text-hi); font-weight: 500; }
.hero-meta .tag{
  display:inline-block;
  background: rgba(94,231,255,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(94,231,255,0.25);
  color: var(--cyan);
  font-size: 11px;
  padding: 3px 9px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  margin: 3px 4px 3px 0;
}

.scroll-cue{
  position:absolute;
  bottom: 28px; left: 24px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-low);
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
}
.scroll-cue .arrow{ animation: bob 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes bob{ 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);} 50%{transform:translateY(5px);} }

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  *{ animation-duration: 0.001ms !important; animation-iteration-count: 1 !important; transition-duration: 0.001ms !important; }
}

/* ============ Section scaffolding ============ */
section.module{
  padding: 90px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(28px);
  transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
}
section.module.in-view{ opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

.module-head{
  display:flex;
  align-items:baseline;
  gap: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.module-index{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--violet);
  border: 1px solid rgba(155,109,255,0.35);
  background: rgba(155,109,255,0.07);
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 7px;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.module-head h2{ font-size: 1.7rem; color: var(--text-hi); }
.module-sub{
  color: var(--text-mid);
  max-width: 680px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.module-sub strong{ color: var(--text-hi); }

/* Think-first prompt box */
.think-box{
  border: 1px dashed rgba(255,209,102,0.4);
  background: rgba(255,209,102,0.04);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 18px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
  color: var(--text-mid);
}
.think-box .lbl{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--warn);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  display:block;
}

/* Code reveal card */
.code-card{
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  background: var(--panel);
  overflow:hidden;
  margin-bottom: 26px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.01), 0 20px 50px -30px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}
.code-card-header{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 12px 18px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
}
.code-card-title{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.dot-row{ display:flex; gap:6px; }
.dot-row span{ width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; }
.dot-row span:nth-child(1){ background:#ff6b6b44; }
.dot-row span:nth-child(2){ background:#ffd16644; }
.dot-row span:nth-child(3){ background:#5cffb044; }

.reveal-btn{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--cyan);
  background: rgba(94,231,255,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(94,231,255,0.3);
  padding: 7px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: var(--transition);
  letter-spacing: .04em;
}
.reveal-btn:hover{ background: rgba(94,231,255,0.18); box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(94,231,255,0.25); }
.reveal-btn:focus-visible{ outline: 2px solid var(--cyan); outline-offset: 2px; }
.reveal-btn.revealed{ color: var(--text-low); border-color: var(--panel-border); background: transparent; }

.code-body-wrap{
  position: relative;
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height .5s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
}
.code-body-wrap.open{ max-height: 2200px; }

.code-veil{
  position:absolute; inset:0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--code-bg) 0%, var(--code-bg) 60%, transparent 100%);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  z-index: 5;
  transition: opacity .4s ease;
  cursor:pointer;
}
.code-veil.hidden-veil{ opacity:0; pointer-events:none; }
.code-veil-content{
  text-align:center;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  color: var(--text-low);
  font-size: 13px;
}
.code-veil-content .icon{ font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; display:block; }

pre.code-body{
  margin:0;
  padding: 20px 22px;
  background: var(--code-bg);
  color: #d6deff;
  font-size: 13.5px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  overflow-x: auto;
  white-space: pre;
}
.tok-kw{ color: #ff79c6; }
.tok-fn{ color: #5ee7ff; }
.tok-str{ color: #ffd166; }
.tok-num{ color: #9b6dff; }
.tok-com{ color: #5c6688; font-style: italic; }
.tok-builtin{ color: #5cffb0; }

/* Explanation accordion-ish block, appears after reveal */
.explain{
  border-top: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  padding: 20px 22px 22px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.012);
  display:none;
}
.explain.show{ display:block; animation: fade-up .5s ease; }
@keyframes fade-up{ from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(8px);} to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);} }
.explain h4{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--cyan);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.explain p{ color: var(--text-mid); margin: 0 0 12px 0; }
.explain ul{ margin: 0 0 12px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: var(--text-mid); }
.explain li{ margin-bottom: 6px; }
.explain code{
  background: rgba(94,231,255,0.08);
  color: var(--cyan);
  padding: 2px 6px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font-size: 0.92em;
}

.callout{
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-size: .94rem;
  margin: 14px 0;
  border-left: 3px solid;
}
.callout.bug{ background: rgba(255,107,129,0.07); border-color: var(--error); color:#ffd6db; }
.callout.tip{ background: rgba(92,255,176,0.06); border-color: var(--success); color:#cfffe6; }
.callout.note{ background: rgba(94,231,255,0.06); border-color: var(--cyan); color:#d8f6ff; }
.callout strong{ display:block; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; margin-bottom: 6px; }

/* Self-check quiz */
.quiz{
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 18px 20px;
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  margin-top: 8px;
}
.quiz .q{ font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text-hi); }
.quiz-opts{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
.quiz-opt{
  text-align:left;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: .94rem;
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  color: var(--text-mid);
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 9px;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition: var(--transition);
}
.quiz-opt:hover{ border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--text-hi); }
.quiz-opt.correct{ border-color: var(--success); background: rgba(92,255,176,0.08); color:#cfffe6; }
.quiz-opt.wrong{ border-color: var(--error); background: rgba(255,107,129,0.08); color:#ffd6db; }
.quiz-fb{ margin-top: 10px; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text-mid); display:none; }
.quiz-fb.show{ display:block; }

/* progress checklist sidebar-ish, inline marker per module */
.done-marker{
  margin-left:auto;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-low);
}
.done-marker.complete{ color: var(--success); }

/* Demo section */
.demo-section{
  padding: 90px 0 120px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
}
.demo-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
  gap: 40px;
  align-items:start;
  margin-top: 30px;
}
@media (max-width: 800px){ .demo-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

#board{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 360px;
}
.cell{
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 2.6rem;
  color: var(--text-hi);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition: var(--transition);
  position: relative;
}
.cell:hover:not(.taken){ border-color: var(--cyan); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(94,231,255,0.18) inset; }
.cell.taken{ cursor: default; }
.cell .mark-x{ color: var(--cyan); text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(94,231,255,0.5); }
.cell .mark-o{ color: var(--magenta); text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,94,192,0.5); }
.cell.win{ background: rgba(92,255,176,0.1); border-color: var(--success); }

.demo-status{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  margin: 18px 0;
  min-height: 20px;
}
.demo-controls{ display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.btn{
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12.5px;
  padding: 9px 16px;
  border-radius: 9px;
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  background: var(--panel);
  color: var(--text-mid);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition: var(--transition);
}
.btn:hover{ border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--text-hi); }
.btn.primary{ border-color: rgba(94,231,255,0.4); color: var(--cyan); background: rgba(94,231,255,0.06); }

.console-panel{
  background: var(--code-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 18px 20px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12.5px;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  max-height: 380px;
  overflow-y: auto;
}
.console-panel .line{ margin-bottom: 4px; }
.console-panel .line.sys{ color: var(--text-low); }
.console-panel .line.x{ color: var(--cyan); }
.console-panel .line.o{ color: var(--magenta); }
.console-panel .line.win{ color: var(--success); }

.map-table{
  width:100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12.5px;
  margin: 14px 0 4px;
}
.map-table th, .map-table td{
  border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  padding: 8px 10px;
  text-align:left;
  color: var(--text-mid);
}
.map-table th{ color: var(--text-hi); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }

footer{
  padding: 50px 0 70px;
  text-align:center;
  color: var(--text-low);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12.5px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="progress-bar"></div>
<nav>
  <div class="nav-pill"><span class="nav-dot"></span> <span id="nav-status">SYSTEM BEREIT</span></div>
</nav>

<div class="wrap">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bracket">[</span> CODE-LERNPFAD <span class="bracket">]</span> Python &rarr; Spiellogik</div>
    <h1>Wie baut man eine <span class="grad">TicTacToe-KI</span> aus zehn kleinen Funktionen?</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Du bekommst keinen fertigen Vortrag, sondern ein Labor. Jeder Codeblock ist standardmäßig abgedeckt &mdash;
      du analysierst ihn zuerst selbst, deckst ihn dann auf und vergleichst deine Vermutung mit der Erklärung.
      Am Ende spielst du dein eigenes Programm live im Browser, als JavaScript-Portierung desselben Algorithmus.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-board-stage">
      <div class="circuit-board" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 220 220">
          <line class="circuit-cell-line" x1="73" y1="10" x2="73" y2="210"/>
          <line class="circuit-cell-line" x1="147" y1="10" x2="147" y2="210"/>
          <line class="circuit-cell-line" x1="10" y1="73" x2="210" y2="73"/>
          <line class="circuit-cell-line" x1="10" y1="147" x2="210" y2="147"/>
          <path class="circuit-trace" d="M 38 38 L 38 182"/>
          <path class="circuit-trace" d="M 110 38 L 110 182"/>
          <path class="circuit-trace v" d="M 38 38 L 182 38"/>
          <path class="circuit-trace v" d="M 38 110 L 182 110"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="38" cy="38" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="110" cy="38" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="182" cy="38" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="38" cy="110" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="110" cy="110" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="182" cy="110" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="38" cy="182" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="110" cy="182" r="6"/>
          <circle class="circuit-node" cx="182" cy="182" r="6"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div><strong>Voraussetzungen:</strong> Listen, Funktionen, while-Schleifen, Grundidee von Minimax/Spielbäumen.</div>
        <div style="margin-top:10px;">
          <span class="tag">9 Funktionen</span>
          <span class="tag">Konsole &rarr; Browser</span>
          <span class="tag">Live-Demo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scroll-cue"><span class="arrow">&darr;</span> Scrollen, um das Spielfeld zu initialisieren</div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= MODULE 1 ================= -->
  <section class="module" id="m1" data-module>
    <div class="module-head">
      <span class="module-index">01 / 09</span>
      <h2>Der Spielzustand: eine Liste mit neun Strings</h2>
      <span class="done-marker" data-marker>&#9675; offen</span>
    </div>
    <p class="module-sub">
      Bevor irgendeine Logik existiert, braucht das Spiel ein <strong>Gedächtnis</strong>: einen Ort, an dem steht,
      was gerade auf dem Brett liegt. TicTacToe hat 9 Felder &mdash; die naheliegendste Datenstruktur dafür ist eine Liste.
    </p>

    <div class="think-box">
      <span class="lbl">&#9888; Bevor du aufdeckst</span>
      Wie würdest <em>du</em> ein leeres 3&times;3-Feld in Python speichern? Reicht eine einzige Liste mit 9 Einträgen,
      oder bräuchtest du eine 3&times;3-Matrix (Liste von Listen)? Überlege kurz, bevor du weiterliest.
    </div>

    <div class="code-card">
      <div class="code-card-header">
        <div class="code-card-title"><span class="dot-row"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span> spielfeld.py</div>
        <button class="reveal-btn" data-reveal="c1">Code aufdecken</button>
      </div>
      <div class="code-body-wrap" data-wrap="c1">
        <div class="code-veil" data-veil="c1">
          <div class="code-veil-content"><span class="icon">&#9608;&#9608;&#9608;</span>1 Zeile Code &mdash; klicke auf &bdquo;Code aufdecken&ldquo;</div>
        </div>
        <pre class="code-body"><span class="tok-fn">field</span> = [<span class="tok-str">" "</span> <span class="tok-kw">for</span> _ <span class="tok-kw">in</span> <span class="tok-builtin">range</span>(<span class="tok-num">9</span>)]</pre>
        <div class="explain" data-explain="c1">
          <h4>Was hier passiert</h4>
          <p>
            Das ist eine <strong>List Comprehension</strong>: eine kompakte Schreibweise für &bdquo;erzeuge eine Liste, indem du
            einen Ausdruck mehrmals wiederholst&ldquo;. <code>range(9)</code> liefert die Zahlen 0 bis 8, also läuft die
            Schleife neunmal &mdash; und bei jedem Durchlauf wird <code>" "</code> (ein Leerzeichen als Platzhalter für &bdquo;leeres Feld&ldquo;)
            an die Liste angehängt. Das Ergebnis: <code>[" ", " ", " ", " ", " ", " ", " ", " ", " "]</code>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Die Indizes 0&ndash;8 entsprechen den neun Brettpositionen, gelesen von links oben nach rechts unten:
          </p>
          <table class="map-table">
            <tr><th>0</th><th>1</th><th>2</th></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td>4</td><td>5</td></tr>
            <tr><td>6</td><td>7</td><td>8</td></tr>
          </table>
          <div class="callout note">
            <strong>Design-Entscheidung</strong>
            Eine flache 1D-Liste statt einer 3&times;3-Matrix zu nutzen ist bewusst einfach gehalten: kein verschachteltes Indizieren
            (<code>field[row][col]</code>), dafür muss man bei Gewinnprüfungen und Ausgabe selbst wissen, welcher Index zu welcher
            Position gehört. Das ist der Tradeoff, den dieser Code eingeht.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

